{"tid":570410,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[再度集氣] 聽日出街見到我地可以講聲加油！","createTime":"2018-02-23T15:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T04:54:19.000Z","uid":171929,"like":77,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d02cca05f450faef39b3de0b5e7b7ce9de6c0014","tid":570410,"uid":171929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"話說小弟同兩位朋友參加咗Red Bull嘅Can you make it 2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係之前一班巴絲打集氣幫手投票嘅情況下，我地成功入圍香港區決賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/223852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F223852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=69860153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日，我地三隻乳豬會同其他入圍隊伍參加香港版嘅Can you make it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遊走港九新界完成唔同嘅任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過程中，所有錢，信用卡同埋智能裝置 (e.g. 手機、平板電腦)都會比人沒收，只可以用手上嘅Red Bull作為貨幣同人換取所需物資，完成全日嘅挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/222519_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F222519_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b250c436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(我地尋晚係briefing session用四罐red bull同cityu嘅同學換到一個暖包，一盒pocky，一盒飯同埋一個電話號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n如果我地係聽日嘅比賽有好嘅表現，配合之前十分理想嘅投票票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三隻乳豬就會有好大機會代表香港係四月頭去歐洲參加全球性嘅Can You Make It比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/052125_d8ea637376945b022923628920ffe4f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F052125_d8ea637376945b022923628920ffe4f7.jpg&h=88011290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打如果聽日係街上邊有緣相見，歡迎你地過嚟同三隻乳豬以手頭上嘅有用物資換red bull嚟支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再用創意方式係我地件用嚟做街頭賣藝嘅假肌肉衫上邊留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有機會去到歐洲闖盪，我地會帶埋件衫去歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/232211_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F232211_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=32b4b6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，我地開咗一個Instagram page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位巴絲打如果有興趣嘅話，都可以follow我地個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為聽日我地會有一個官方、全程跟住我地嘅runner keep住幫我地upload係香港唔同地方完成一啲任務嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/threelittlepigs_cymi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fthreelittlepigs_cymi%2F&d=3tHkJ1cLXIwBAp0qFSVNvBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6d6ec061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/threelittlepigs_cymi/</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，希望我地聽日就好似我依家飲緊嘅依罐可樂咁：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/224742_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F224742_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=46fa0eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4837f3c8749e640e9aa2701ead5972ccfa523bbd","tid":570410,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":12,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55d7ab82f686ccc2cf4a786241a532ff89e936f8","tid":570410,"uid":7521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:28:38.000Z","msg":"琴日喺city有幾個女仔走埋黎又係用redbull同我地換野 我個friend比左筒mentos佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cf676f4884f51ff097d8d4805a617a92758813","tid":570410,"uid":171929,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"4837f3c8749e640e9aa2701ead5972ccfa523bbd","tid":570410,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":12,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"我地平均身高應該過170cm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企隻貓垂直身高就應該有170<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">mm</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/234840_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F234840_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b5347a43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7822776df87695feab3df0c61d9cf7faa37b5228","tid":570410,"uid":171929,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55d7ab82f686ccc2cf4a786241a532ff89e936f8","tid":570410,"uid":7521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:28:38.000Z","msg":"琴日喺city有幾個女仔走埋黎又係用redbull同我地換野 我個friend比左筒mentos佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打同埋你朋友支持我地依排大學生玩依個活動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b072b56a2b98cd83e37142d606cc2bbe049f2d","tid":570410,"uid":88102,