es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"巴打，你唔講我都唔為意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThanks for your support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3aadff4203fd8d74dbe5f5062df1f8cb2a46954","tid":570410,"uid":171929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:00:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/565996/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/565996/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/562669/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/562669/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，之前係依兩個post留過名支持我地嘅巴絲打唔洗擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我地去到歐洲闖蕩，一定會寫埋你地個名同留言係對翼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對翼都整埋傢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/005934_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F005934_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6c2bfeec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eab80ba4d609c03eb491d506d7e52c79884684ec","tid":570410,"uid":123166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"係巴打你之前旅遊台個po留過言，希望你去得成啦～<br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"cfa5d3d0b29e0ce59997692189695cf4dba1f3e3","tid":570410,"uid":111181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:59:15.000Z","msg":"聽日1130放學<br />\n咁早你地開始未？"},{"pid":"d41ef75a5aa4446ff12629e70044e352b96198b9","tid":570410,"uid":100169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T20:42:38.000Z","msg":"見到兩個大soc房既面孔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9013190c97330f25e434cf95e744b2ba7a425b3","tid":570410,"uid":417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T21:36:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3546700995a196942ca9dbf7f66641374421e422","tid":570410,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T22:25:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"760a914866fa534a3f298b80ffa9a8fe8a6aefd8","tid":570410,"uid":135313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"其實個比賽係做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我收埋啲錢係底褲or搵人做馬用錢換你啲red bull咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db2ec9a14250ad1e6f9b3a0d56e3c3842b1d3e1","tid":570410,"uid":171929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:07:38.000Z","msg":"早晨咁多位巴絲打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今朝臨出門口，就有好預兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宿舍清潔姨姨係我臨走前比咗封利是我，祝我學業進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/100031_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F100031_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7e45704d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然今次比賽唔係好關學業事，但我地都唔會辜負清潔姨姨依封利是嘅好意頭，會儘力攞好成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（由於比賽期間唔可以用現金嘅關係，我好快就拆咗嚟買老麥早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"e8b4e52c808f9d21ce9e88029687861c4272a096","tid":570410,"uid":171929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eab80ba4d609c03eb491d506d7e52c79884684ec","tid":570410,"uid":123166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"係巴打你之前旅遊台個po留過言，希望你去得成啦～<br />\n<br />\n加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打係依兩個post都咁支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90222ff2d987e00a8b621c0b4f2abc8fbdc136e","tid":570410,"uid":171929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa5d3d0b29e0ce59997692189695cf4dba1f3e3","tid":570410,"uid":111181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:59:15.000Z","msg":"聽日1130放學<br />\n咁早你地開始未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"我地應該會12：30開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有緣係街上見啦巴打，因為我地係途中唔可以用手機同外界聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地唔會唔記得你係之前個post想托我地帶你架模型飛機同我地去歐洲闖蕩傢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09b2bce72352a42673fc2fb756a1eac0a42005a","tid":570410,"uid":111181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e90222ff2d987e00a8b621c0b4f2abc8fbdc136e","tid":570410,"uid":171929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa5d3d0b29e0ce59997692189695cf4dba1f3e3","tid":570410,"uid":111181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:59:15.000Z","msg":"聽日1130放學<br />\n咁早你地開始未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"我地應該會12：30開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有緣係街上見啦巴打，因為我地係途中唔可以用手機同外界聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地唔會唔記得你係之前個post想托我地帶你架模型飛機同我地去歐洲闖蕩傢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:16:20.000Z","msg":"模乜鬼型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   出